<h1>decorating cupcakes</h1>

<div id="content">
		
	<div id="content_middle">
	<p>Decorating cupcakes has never been easier with these simple and fun cupcake decorating techniques. Here you will find everything you need to know to create perfectly decorated cupcakes – from choosing the right type of icing to creating delicious fillings and using a variety of candies for cupcake decorations!</p>
	</div>
	
	<div id="middle_features" class="aligned_boxes">
	
	<div id="column1">
		
		<div class="box">
			<div class="header"><h3>cupcake decorating basics</h3></div>
			<div class="content">
				<div class="sidelong"><img src="/images/cupcake/sideimages/cupcake_decorating-basics.jpg" alt="Learn the basics of decorating cupcakes" width="100" height="100"></div>
				<p>Choose the right cupcake decorating bag and fill it properly. See how to hold and squeeze the bag for perfectly-formed cupcake decorations.</p>
				<ul>
				<li><a href="/decorating/decorating-basics/using-decorating-bags.cfm">How to choose decorating bags</a></li>
				<li><a href="/decorating/decorating-basics/filling-decorating-bags.cfm">Filling the decorating bag</a></li>
				<li><a href="/decorating/decorating-basics/folding-parchment-triangles.cfm">Folding parchment triangles</a></li>
				<li><a href="/decorating/decorating-basics/pressure-control.cfm">Pressure control</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div><!-- /content -->
		</div>

		<div class="box">
			<div class="header"><h3>icing recipes for decorating cupcakes</h3></div>
			<div class="content">
				<div class="sidelong"><img src="/images/cupcake/sideimages/cupcake_icing-recipes.jpg" alt="Get icing recipes for cupcake decorating" width="100" height="100"></div>
				<p>Once the cupcake is baked and cooled, it’s time for cupcake decorating fun. The icing options and flavors for decorated cupcakes are limitless.</p>
				<ul>
				<li><a href="/recipes/browse.cfm?cat=Icing">All icing recipes</a></li>
			  	</ul>
			</div><!-- /content -->
		</div>

		<div class="box">
			<div class="header"><h3>icing consistency for decorated cupcakes</h3></div>
			<div class="content">
				<div class="sidelong"><img src="/images/cupcake/sideimages/cupcake_icing-consistancy.jpg" alt="Choose the right icing consistency for decorated cupcakes" width="100" height="100"></div>
				<p>Different icing finishes for cupcake decorating can be achieved by changing its consistency.</p>
				<ul>
				<li><a href="/decorating/icing/icing-consistency.cfm">Icing consistency</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div><!-- /content -->
		</div>

		<div class="box">
			<div class="header"><h3>covering the cupcakes & decorating</h3></div>
			<div class="content">
				<div class="sidelong"><img src="/images/cupcake/sideimages/cupcake_covering-cupcake.jpg" alt="Covering and decorating cupcakes with icing & fondant" width="100" height="100"></div>
				<p>You can be as fancy as you want when decorating cupcakes with icing, fondant or candy melts.</p>
				<ul>
				<li><a href="/technique/1M-Swirl">Making 1M swirls</a></li>
				<li><a href="/decorating/cupcake-decorating/icing-cupcakes-with-a-spatula.cfm">Icing cupcakes with a spatula</a></li>
				<li><a href="/technique/Covering-the-Cupcake-Using-Ganache-Candy-Melts">Covering a cupcake using ganache & candy melts</a></li>
				<li><a href="/decorating/cupcake-decorating/covering-cupcake-with-rolled-fondant.cfm">Covering a cupcake with rolled fondant</a></li>
	            <li><a href="/decorating/cupcake-decorating/covering-cupcake-with-poured-fondant.cfm">Covering a cupcake with poured fondant</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div><!-- /content -->
		</div>

	</div> <!-- end column 1 -->
	
	<div id="column2">

		<div class="box">
			<div class="header"><h3>types of icing for decorating cupcakes</h3></div>
			<div class="content">
				<div class="sidelong"><img src="/images/cupcake/sideimages/cupcake_icing.jpg" alt="Choose from various types of icing for cupcake decorating" width="100" height="100"></div>
				<p>You can definitely make a unique statement with your cupcake desserts just by choosing different icing for cupcake decorating.</p>
				<ul>
				<li><a href="/decorating/icing/icing-chart.cfm">Types of icing</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div><!-- /content -->
		</div>

		<div class="box">
			<div class="header"><h3>coloring icing and fondant for cupcake decorations</h3></div>
			<div class="content">
				<div class="sidelong"><img src="/images/cupcake/sideimages/cupcake_coloring-icing.jpg" alt="Learn how to color icing & fondant for cupcake decorating" width="100" height="100"></div>
				<p>Choosing the right color should help set the theme and personalize your cupcake decorating. Color is part of all celebrations!</p>
				<ul>
				<li><a href="/decorating/fondant/coloring-fondant.cfm">Coloring and flavoring fondant</a></li>
				<li><a href="/decorating/icing/coloring-icing.cfm">Coloring icing</a></li>
				<li><a href="/decorating/icing/icing-color-chart.cfm">Color chart</a></li>
				<li><a href="/decorating/icing/tips-on-coloring-icing.cfm">Tips on coloring icing</a></li>																												
				</ul>
			</div><!-- /content -->
		</div>

		<div class="box">
			<div class="header"><h3>filling the cupcakes & decorating</h3></div>
			<div class="content">
				<div class="sidelong"><img src="/images/cupcake/sideimages/cupcake_filling.jpg" alt="Decorating cupcakes with delicious fillings" width="100" height="100"></div>
				<p>You can really have fun with flavor and cupcake decorating when you add a tasty icing, filling or jam to your baked cupcakes.</p>
				<ul>
				<li><a href="/cupcakes/making-cupcakes/icing-filled-cupcakes.cfm">Icing filled center</a></li>
				<li><a href="/cupcakes/making-cupcakes/jam-filled-cupcakes.cfm">Jam filled center</a></li>
				<li><a href="/recipes/browse.cfm?cat=Cupcakes&cat2=Cupcake-Fillings">Cupcake filling recipes</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div><!-- /content -->
		</div>

		<div class="box">
			<div class="header"><h3>cupcake decorating techniques</h3></div>
			<div class="content">
				<div class="sidelong"><img src="/images/cupcake/sideimages/cupcake_decorating-techniqu.jpg" alt="Learn simple & fun cupcake decorating techniques" width="100" height="100"></div>
				<p>You can change the look of your cupcakes by using a clever combination of techniques for decorating cupcakes.</p>
				<ul>
				<li><a href="/decorating/browse.cfm?cat=Buttercream-Icing">Decorating with buttercream</a></li>
				<li><a href="/decorating/browse.cfm?cat=Fondant-Gum-Paste">Decorating with fondant & gum paste</a></li>
				<li><a href="/decorating/browse.cfm?cat=Royal-Icing">Decorating with royal icing</a></li>
				<li><a href="/decorating/browse.cfm?cat=Candies">Decorating with candy</a></li>	
				</ul>
			</div><!-- /content -->
		</div>

	</div> <!-- end column 2 -->

